name: Insomnia, World #11
description:
| Insomnia |
|Behind each window there's one of us, aren't we all the same when it happens? Paths would differ as we go along, as he went along, still, her shadows would look the same. The boy felt numb trying to grab on what was not of his possession. " It has been quite a journey in pursuit of distractions. It was at this moment when I finally realized that it's all a distraction, materiality feels non-existent and morality is intangible." The journal said.
